snippet.title: THIRSTY SUITORS | Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
We're serving up Thirsty Suitors for Xbox, PlayStation, Switch, and PC on November 2nd. Wishlist on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1617220/?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=AIShowcase2023&utm_medium=web

Can Jala learn to love herself and heal the wounds of her past? Thirsty Suitors is a stylish, story-driven adventure that unfolds through turn-based battles, skateboarding, and cooking.

Developed by OUTERLOOP GAMES. Published by Annapurna Interactive. 

© Annapurna Interactive, 2023
